{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782713916415,"sessionID":"ses_0edf92fdcffeIVMHfhZkGdAVyf","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_UVrl7cQhw0I3ClYlmNFdyYmw","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.json","limit":520,"offset":2388},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n2388:           \"manualEvidence\": [\n2389:             {\n2390:               \"kind\": \"manual-review\",\n2391:               \"detail\": \"The source and translated profile routes both keep the profile image as static packaged media without viewer behavior.\"\n2392:             }\n2393:           ]\n2394:         },\n2395:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\n2396:       }\n2397:     },\n2398:     {\n2399:       \"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-profi-c34aae0a57-002-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o\",\n2400:       \"featureName\": \"Navigation surface, menu, drawer, toolbar, or tab command behavior.\",\n2401:       \"sourcePath\": \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/profile/Profile.kt\",\n2402:       \"importance\": \"critical\",\n2403:       \"category\": \"kotlin-source\",\n2404:       \"riskTags\": [\n2405:         \"image_viewer\",\n2406:         \"navigation_resource\",\n2407:         \"permissions\",\n2408:         \"state_model\"\n2409:       ],\n2410:       \"keyClasses\": [],\n2411:       \"keyMethods\": [\n2412:         \"Profile\"\n2413:       ],\n2414:       \"androidIds\": [],\n2415:       \"dependencies\": [],\n2416:       \"featurePoint\": \"Navigation surface, menu, drawer, toolbar, or tab command behavior.\",\n2417:       \"sourceEvidence\": \"path=app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/profile/Profile.kt; category=kotlin-source; importance=critical; keyMethods=Profile; featurePoint=Navigation surface, menu, drawer, toolbar, or tab command behavior.\",\n2418:       \"status\": \"implemented\",\n2419:       \"plannedPhase\": \"phase-06-profile-capabilities-verification\",\n2420:       \"sourceBehavior\": \"`Profile.kt` renders a back command, static profile action cards, and a logout button. The back arrow calls `navController.navigateUp()`, the action cards keep placeholder click handlers, and logout clears the start destination stack before routing to onboarding.\",\n2421:       \"targetBehavior\": \"`profile_route_service.cj` now centralizes the profile-specific back-route decision, explicit edit/section placeholder action messages, and logout transition state, while `renderProfileRoute` preserves the visible back affordance, static action cards, and logout button. `bootstrap_page.cj` delegates the profile logout flow and typed profile action callbacks to the focused profile transition/service endpoints before routing to onboarding after session logout.\",\n2422:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\n2423:         \"Manual source review confirmed `Profile.kt` owns the back icon, edit/action-card click surfaces, and logout navigation callback.\",\n2424:         \"Manual target review confirmed `profile_route_service.cj::resolveBackRoute`, `::canNavigateBack`, `::buildLogoutTransition`, `::editActionMessage`, and `::sectionActionMessage` now carry the profile-specific command wiring instead of closing the row through only the broad bootstrap shell.\",\n2425:         \"`profile_page.cj::buildProfileTopBar`, `::buildProfileSection`, and `::renderProfileRoute` preserve the visible back/logout/action-card surface while `profile_store.cj::logoutRoute`, `::actionFeedbackMessage`, and `::sectionFeedbackMessage` keep the route/message state explicit.\",\n2426:         \"Final-coverage test build report PASS: `translation-inputs/test-build-reports/final-coverage/test-build-report.md` ran `cjpm test --target aarch64-linux-ohos` from `entry/src/test/cangjie` successfully.\",\n2427:         \"Phase-06 build gate PAS